      • onDestroy

        public void onDestroy()

      • onProgressChange

        public void onProgressChange(android.location.Location location,
                             RouteProgress routeProgress)
        Listener used to update the location on screen and the data in the top / bottom views of the drop-in UI.

        Added to com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.MapboxNavigation.

        Parameters:
        location - modified to snap to the route being driven
        routeProgress - used to create new models for our top / bottom views
        Since:
        0.6.0

      • userOffRoute

        public void userOffRoute(android.location.Location location)
        Listener used to update when a user has gone off-route.

        This is being used as a cue for a re-route UX / to fetch a new route to keep the user on course.

        Added to com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.MapboxNavigation.

        Parameters:
        location - given to create a new origin
        Since:
        0.6.0

      • onMilestoneEvent

        public void onMilestoneEvent(RouteProgress routeProgress,
                             java.lang.String instruction,
                             Milestone milestone)
        Listener used to play instructions and finish this activity when the arrival milestone is triggered.

        Added to com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.MapboxNavigation.

        Parameters:
        routeProgress - ignored in this scenario
        instruction - to be voiced by the InstructionPlayer
        milestone - the milestone being triggered
        Since:
        0.8.0

      • onRunning

        public void onRunning(boolean running)
        Listener used to determine is navigation is running / not running.

        In NavigationView, views will be shown when true. When false, the Activity will be destroyed.

        Parameters:
        running - true if MapboxNavigation is up and running, false if not
        Since:
        0.6.0

      • fasterRouteFound

        public void fasterRouteFound(com.mapbox.api.directions.v5.models.DirectionsRoute directionsRoute)
        Listener that will be fired if a faster DirectionsRoute is found while navigating.
        Parameters:
        directionsRoute - faster route retrieved
        Since:
        0.9.0

        public void updateFeedback(FeedbackItem feedbackItem)
